	    Export compliance: LingoLoop only uses Apple-provided HTTPS /
	    standard system encryption — no proprietary crypto. Declaring
	    this here makes App Store Connect skip the per-build export
	    compliance questionnaire on every TestFlight / App Store
	    submission.
